categories: Category:Moffs and Grand Moffs of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Unidentified Moff was a male Moff of the Sith Empire living during the Galactic War. Around 3643 BBY he began seeing a Twi'lek girl named Tivva. Due to the difference in their ages, Tivva's sister Vette was highly squicked by their relationship.
Unidentified Moff is mentioned in Star Wars: The Old Republic during Vette's companion mission.
